4, its topline contraction continued due to weak volume and unfavorable pricing across most parts of the business. I expect this to</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1349030861/image_1349030861.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741518-sealed-air-stock-on-sidelines-until-recovery-becomes-clear", "pub_date": "2024-12-02 19:39:13"}, {"id": "4741517", "title": "EVF: Lacks Appeal In Today's Environment", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1304022517/image_1304022517.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Chess game on chess board behind business man background. Business concept to present financial information and marketing strategy analysis. Investment target in global economy and digital commercial.\" data-id=\"1304022517\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1304022517/image_1304022517.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1304022517/image_1304022517.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1304022517/image_1304022517.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1304022517/image_1304022517.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1304022517/image_1304022517.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1304022517/image_1304022517.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1304022517/image_1304022517.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1304022517/image_1304022517.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc