getty_images/1351375648/image_1351375648.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1351375648/image_1351375648.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">FerreiraSilva</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Petr\u00f3leo Brasileiro S.A. - Petrobras (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/PBR\" title=\"Petr\u00f3leo Brasileiro S.A. - Petrobras\">PBR</a></span>) investors have endured a challenging third quarter as the stock of Brazil's leading oil and gas company stuttered. I assess that PBR has failed to emerge decisively from its consolidation zone, even though</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1351375648/image_1351375648.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741474-petrobras-theres-still-time-to-buy-this-on-the-cheap", "pub_date": "2024-12-02 19:30:43"}, {"id": "4741515", "title": "ONEOK: Benefitting From Recent Acquisitions", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200436389/image_200436389.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"USA, Texas, Midland, Permian Basin Petroleum Museum, dusk\" data-id=\"200436389-001\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1022px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200436389/image_200436389.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200436389/image_200436389.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200436389/image_200436389.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200436389/image_200436389.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200436389/image_200436389.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200436389/image_200436389.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200436389/image_200436389.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200436389/image_200436389.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\">USA, Texas, Midland, Permian Basin Petroleum, dusk</p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Walter Bibikow/DigitalVision via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>I\u2019m not enthusiastic about seeing my EnLink units (which have been earning a strong free cash flow) diluted into a larger company. I view the acquisition of EnLink (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ENLC\" title=\"EnLink Midstream, LLC\">ENLC</a>) by ONEOK (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/OKE\" title=\"ONEOK, Inc.\">OKE</a></span>) as net negative for EnLink</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200436389/image_200436389.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741515-oneok-benefitting-from-recent-acquisitions-oke-enlc-stock", "pub_date": "2024-12-02 19:15:49"}, {"id": "4741512", "title": "Rocket Pharmaceuticals: Not Bad Valuation But Reflexivity Risks Remain", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148853421/image_2148853421.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Woman, computer screen and dna \u200bfor lab research or gene therapy or anti aging science, futuristic or innovation. Female person, pointing and double helix for medical tech, chromosome or chemistry\" data-id=\"2148853421\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1069px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148853421/image_2148853421.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148853421/image_2148853421.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148853421/image_2148853421.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148853421/image_2148853421.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148853421/image_2148853421.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148853421/image_2148853421.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148853421/image_2148853421.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148853421/image_2148853421.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Bevan Goldswain/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><strong>Rocket Pharmaceuticals</strong> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/RCKT\" title=\"Rocket Pharmaceuticals, Inc.\">RCKT</a></span>) actually looks relatively attractive. While prevalence figures are a little unusable because in principle gene therapies shouldn't have frequent doses, incidence figures are provided, and at the bottom of the range of recorded</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148853421/image_2148853421.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741512-rocket-pharmaceuticals-not-bad-valuation-but-reflexivity-risks-remain", "pub_date": "2024-12-02 19:08:58"}, {"id": "4741409", "title": "I'm Buying Up To 9% Yield For Recurring Income", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1495778213/image_1495778213.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"9 percentage sign isolated on white background. 9 percent off 3d. 9 percent sign. 3D rendering.\" data-id=\"1495778213\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1253px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1495778213/image_1495778213.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1495778213/image_1495778213.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1495778213/image_1495778213.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1495778213/image_1495778213.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1495778213/image_1495778213.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1495778213/image_1495778213.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1495778213/image_1495778213.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1495778213/image_1495778213.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Vivek Vishwakarma</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>This year has been full of ups and downs for stocks, to say the least, and with Thanksgiving now in the rearview mirror, it\u2019s time to look for bargains as we get ready the holiday season and the end of</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1495778213/image_1495778213.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741409-im-buying-up-to-9-percent-yield-for-recurring-income", "pub_date": "2024-12-02 19:00:00"}, {"id": "4741508", "title": "Tesla's Upcoming Government Double-Whammy", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1542588811/image_1542588811.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"An electric car plugged in against a background of a rural location at sunset\" data-id=\"1542588811\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1021px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1542588811/image_1542588811.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1542588811/image_1542588811.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1542588811/image_1542588811.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1542588811/image_1542588811.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1542588811/image_1542588811.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1542588811/image_1542588811.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1542588811/image_1542588811.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1542588811/image_1542588811.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Justin Paget</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><b>Tesla, Inc.</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TSLA\" title=\"Tesla, Inc.\">TSLA</a></span>) is a company that, we believe, is heavily overvalued, as discussed in our large article, where we shared how the company's share price run-up <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4735229-tesla-election-victory-doesnt-change-core-concerns\">doesn't change the core concerns</a>. As we'll see</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1542588811/image_1542588811.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741508-tesla-upcoming-government-double-whammy", "pub_date": "2024-12-02 18:52:15"}, {"id": "4741506", "title": "SPYD: High-Yield Might Have More Risk Than Benefit", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1795167728/image_1795167728.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"growth in business and finance, growing graphs and charts\" data-id=\"1795167728\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1795167728/image_1795167728.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1795167728/image_1795167728.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1795167728/image_1795167728.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1795167728/image_1795167728.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1795167728/image_1795167728.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1795167728/image_1795167728.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1795167728/image_1795167728.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1